question.title: Failed to execute goal org.apache.maven.plugins:maven-compiler-plugin:3.8.0:compile (default-compile) on project
question.body:

Failed to execute goal org.apache.maven.plugins:maven-compiler-plugin:3.8.0:compile (default-compile) on project:Compilation Failure -> org.apache.maven.lifecycle.LifecycleExecutionException: at org.apache.maven.lifecycle.internal.MojoExecutor.doExecute (MojoExecutor.java:206): Caused by : org.apache.maven.plugin.compiler.CompilationFailureException: Compilation failure
